Dear Webmaster,
%p A new booking has been placed on the #{APP_CONFIG[:site_name]} website for the event #{@booking.event_name}.
%p The details are:
%table
  %tr
    %td Name:
    %td="#{@booking.first_name} #{@booking.surname}"
  %tr
    %td Date of birth:
    %td="#{@booking.date_of_birth.to_s(:short_date)}"
  %tr
    %td Gender:
    %td="#{@booking.gender}"
  %tr
    %td Phone number:
    %td="#{@booking.phone_number}"
  %tr
    %td Email address:
    %td="#{@booking.email}"
  %tr
    %td Address line:
    %td="#{@booking.address_string}"
  %tr
    %td Where did you hear about the event?
    %td="#{@booking.where_did_you_hear_about_the_event}"

%p="Please click here for more information: #{APP_CONFIG[:site_url]}/events/#{@booking.event_page_id}"